I did not feel any discomfort. 

Even my kids knew what their dental problem is and what is to be done. She explains very clearly so that they can also understand.. I strongly recommend her

She had 4 to 5 sittings with proper appointments and we didn’t wait for more than 20 minutes in each sittings. Dr. Aarthi Praveen clearly explains what is the issue and what are the options for the crown with the patient and gets their opinion before the treatment. Overall it was a comfortable experience for my wife.
